  "steps": [
    "Prepare 5 ml LB medium with antibiotic resistance and 0.5% ml Tergitol",
    "Inoculate one colony in the prepared LB medium",
    "Add 0.01-1 mM of the desired fatty acid to the culture medium",
    "Inoculate the culture for at least 16 hours at 37 °C",
    "Measure the absorption with a photometer at a wavelength 600 nm",
    "Dilute the culture to an OD 600 of 0.05 with LB medium",
    "Fill a 24 well plate with 800 µl of 3 biological with 3 technically replicats respectively like shown in the table below",
    "%s %s Sample 1.1Sample 1.2Sample 1.3Sample 5.1Sample 5.2Sample 5.3Sample 2.1Sample 2.2Sample 2.3Sample 6.1Sample 6.2Sample 6.3Sample 3.1Sample 3.2Sample 3.3Sample 7.1Sample 7.2Sample 7.3Sample 4.1Sample 4.2Sample 4.3Sample 8.1Sample 8.2Sample 8.3",
    "Inoculate the 24 well plate at 37°C for at least 16 hours",
    "Transfer the samples from the 24 well plate on a 96 well plate like shown in the table below",
